## ParsedIdCookie type

The format of state elements stored in the `id` cookie.

<b>Signature:</b>

```typescript
type ParsedIdCookie = [
    cookieDisabled: string,
    domainUserId: string,
    cookieCreateTs: number,
    visitCount: number,
    nowTs: number,
    lastVisitTs: number | undefined,
    sessionId: string,
    previousSessionId: string,
    firstEventId: string,
    firstEventTs: number | undefined,
    eventIndex: number
];
```
